      undoSt.push(cur); cur+=op[1]; redoSt.length=0; out.push(null);
    } else if(op[0]==='undo'){
      if(undoSt.length){ redoSt.push(cur); cur=undoSt.pop(); }
      out.push(null);
    } else if(op[0]==='redo'){
      if(redoSt.length){ undoSt.push(cur); cur=redoSt.pop(); }
      out.push(null);
    } else { // get
      out.push(cur);
    }
  }
  return out;
}
```

**Edge cases**: Empty undoSt pe undo no-op. Naya type ke baad redo stale isliye clear.

**Complexity**: O(total chars) per op (string concat), O(n) overall states.
